==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suspire
<hw>Sus*pire"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>suspirare</ets> to breathe out, to sigh; <ets>sub</ets> under +
<ets>spirare</ets> to breathe: cf. F. <ets>souspirer</ets>, OF.
<ets>souspirer</ets>.]</ety> <def>To fetch a long, deep breath; to sigh;
to breathe.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Fireflies that <qex>suspire</qex>⟦br⟧
In short, soft lapses of transported flame.</q> <rj><qau>Mrs.
Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suspire</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Suspire
<hw>Sus*pire"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. L.
<ets>suspirium</ets>.]</ety> <def>A long, deep breath; a sigh.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suspired</ent>⟦br⟧
